parameters.query: SELECT pa.id, pa.google_email, ap.external_profile_id, ap.provider FROM pva_accounts pa LEFT JOIN antidetect_profiles ap ON pa.antidetect_profile_id = ap.id WHERE pa.status = 'active' AND (pa.last_warmed_at IS NULL OR pa.last_warmed_at < NOW() - INTERVAL '4 hours') ORDER BY pa.last_warmed_at ASC NULLS FIRST LIMIT 10
UPDATE pva_accounts SET last_warmed_at = NOW(), warming_count = COALESCE(warming_count, 0) + 1 WHERE id = $1
INSERT INTO humanization_logs (account_id, action_type, session_data, executed_at) VALUES ($1, $2, $3, NOW())
